  </div> </div> <div data-meta-title="Single Sign-On (SSO)" class="_slide-inactive-content_nwyw1_108 slide-inactive-content"> <div data-meta-title="Single Sign-On (SSO)" class="_inactive-content-wrap_nwyw1_108 inactive-content-wrap"> <div class="_circle-indicator_nwyw1_108 circle-indicator" data-meta-title="Single Sign-On (SSO)"></div> <div> <h3 data-meta-title="Single Sign-On (SSO)" class="_inactive-content-heading_nwyw1_310 h4-size">Single Sign-On (SSO)</h3> <p class="p-regular"><p>Deliver single sign-on to web, SaaS, mobile, and virtual applications with Workspace ONE® Intelligent Hub.</p></p> </div> </div> </div> </div><div class="_copy-slide_nwyw1_63 slide" data-meta-title="Risk-based conditional access" role="group" aria-label=" slide 4 of 4"> <div class="_slide-active-content_nwyw1_118 slide-active-content"> <div class="_image-wrap_nwyw1_191"> <picture>  <img src="https://static.omnissa.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_image_to_webp/public/2024-09/Omnissa_Product_Omnissa-Access_Features_Conditional_Access_2x.jpg.webp" alt="" width="728" height="729" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="_slide-image_nwyw1_213" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true"> </picture> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" width="398" height="398" viewBox="0 0 398 398" class="_omnissa-design_nwyw1_220">
