  </div> </div> <div data-meta-title="Risk-based conditional access" class="_slide-inactive-content_nwyw1_108 slide-inactive-content"> <div data-meta-title="Risk-based conditional access" class="_inactive-content-wrap_nwyw1_108 inactive-content-wrap"> <div class="_circle-indicator_nwyw1_108 circle-indicator" data-meta-title="Risk-based conditional access"></div> <div> <h3 data-meta-title="Risk-based conditional access" class="_inactive-content-heading_nwyw1_310 h4-size">Risk-based conditional access</h3> <p class="p-regular"><p>Create and implement access policies that leverage device enrollment, network, user behavior, location, and third-party security signals and information.</p></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="_pagination_nwyw1_399"> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="19.807" height="17.934" viewBox="0 0 19.807 17.934" class="_prev_nwyw1_359 prev" data-icon="btn-arrow">  <use  xlink:href="#icon-btn-arrow"></use>   </svg> <div class="_pagination-item_nwyw1_453 pagination-item" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-current="false" aria-label="Go to slide 1" data-meta-title="Access broker"></div><div class="_pagination-item_nwyw1_453 pagination-item" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-current="false" aria-label="Go to slide 2" data-meta-title="Adaptive Multifactor Authentication (MFA) "></div><div class="_pagination-item_nwyw1_453 pagination-item" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-current="false" aria-label="Go to slide 3" data-meta-title="Single Sign-On (SSO)"></div><div class="_pagination-item_nwyw1_453 pagination-item" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-current="false" aria-label="Go to slide 4" data-meta-title="Risk-based conditional access"></div> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="19.807" height="17.934" viewBox="0 0 19.807 17.934" class="_next_nwyw1_360 next" data-icon="btn-arrow">  <use  xlink:href="#icon-btn-arrow"></use>   </svg> </div> </copy-carousel> </section> <copy-list paddingBottom="true"> <section class="_copylist_block_1d29h_49 section-padding-bottom"> <div class="container"> <div class="_copylist_details_1d29h_49 text-center"> <span class="_tag_title_1d29h_49">USE CASES</span> <h2 class="section-heading">Solve your toughest challenges</h2> <p class="_sub_title_1d29h_81 p-lead">Providing consistent access to apps and data without compromising security is challenging. Omnissa Access can help.</p> </div> <div class="_copylist_img_with_text_1d29h_102"> <div class="_cl_left_1d29h_125"> <picture>  <img src="https://static.omnissa.com/sites/default/files/styles/image_to_webp/public/2024-09/Omnissa_Product_Omnissa-Access_Use-Case_Image_2x.jpg.webp" alt="" width="1008" height="1117" loading="lazy" decoding="async" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true"> </picture> </div> <div class="_cl_right_1d29h_175 cl_right"> <div class="_text_block_1d29h_183"> <div class="_copy-list-item_1d29h_1 copy-list-item active"> <h3 class="_heading-title_1d29h_21 heading-title h5-size">Enable zero trust</h3> <p class="_sub-title_1d29h_200 p-small">Balance risk and continuously validate device, user, and application context to deliver least-privilege access to corporate resources. </p>  </div> </div><div class="_text_block_1d29h_183"> <div class="_copy-list-item_1d29h_1 copy-list-item"> <h3 class="_heading-title_1d29h_21 heading-title h5-size">Accelerated app deployments</h3> <p class="_sub-title_1d29h_200 p-small">Provide intrinsically secure, conditional access to any app on any device. Accelerate deployment times by brokering access based on complex identity, device, and app combinations.</p>  </div> </div><div class="_text_block_1d29h_183"> <div class="_copy-list-item_1d29h_1 copy-list-item"> <h3 class="_heading-title_1d29h_21 heading-title h5-size">Single sign-on</h3> <p class="_sub-title_1d29h_200 p-small">Continuously verify user, device, and login context to provide highly secure single sign-on and enable employee productivity while protecting corporate assets.</p>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> </copy-list>   </div><div class="_gradient-background_1cvxe_1"> <div class="_background_1cvxe_5"></div>  <quote-slider paddingTop="true" paddingBottom="true"> <section class="_testimonials-carousel_1gw3g_1 section-padding-top section-padding-bottom"> <div class="container"> <div class="_testimonials-carousel-heading_1gw3g_1 text-center"> <h2 class="_heading-title_1gw3g_1 section-heading">What our customers are saying</h2> </div> </div> <div class="_testimonials-carousel-slider_1gw3g_165 swiper"> <div class="swiper-wrapper"> <div class="swiper-slide"> <div class="_testimonials-carousel-info_1gw3g_169">  <div class="_quote-icon_1gw3g_246"> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="74" height="57" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 74 57" data-icon="quotation-outline">  <symbol id="icon-quotation-outline"><path fill="#fff" d="M66.97 5.841s-13.41-10-23.41.665-1.954 25.5 10.729 27.518c0 0 .419 10.669-7.94 20.243l.554 1.095s26.2-14.227 25.085-38.029"></path><path stroke="#4A12F0" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.3" d="M66.97 5.841s-13.41-10-23.41.665-1.954 25.5 10.729 27.518c0 0 .419 10.669-7.94 20.243l.554 1.095s26.2-14.227 25.085-38.029"></path><path fill="#fff" d="M29.47 5.841s-13.41-10-23.41.665-1.954 25.5 10.729 27.518c0 0 .419 10.669-7.94 20.243l.554 1.095s26.2-14.227 25.085-38.029"></path><path stroke="#4A12F0" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.3" d="M29.47 5.841s-13.41-10-23.41.665-1.954 25.5 10.729 27.518c0 0 .419 10.669-7.94 20.243l.554 1.095s26.2-14.227 25.085-38.029"></path></symbol><use  xlink:href="#icon-quotation-outline"></use>   </svg> </div> <div class="_testimonial-content_1gw3g_183 p-lead"><p class="text-align-justify">“Thanks to Omnissa Access, we now have MFA—something our MDM simply couldn’t support—adding a critical layer of security beyond just usernames and passwords. It’s given us greater confidence in protecting both our users and the bank’s sensitive data.”</p></div> <div class="_testimonial-row_1gw3g_309"> <div class="_testimonial-content-row_1gw3g_322"> <div class="_testimonial-author-title_1gw3g_186"> <div class="_author-name_1gw3g_186"> Uğur Koçer </div> <span class="_position_1gw3g_189 p-regular"> Windows Applications Design and Planning Manager,  Yapi Kredi Technology </span> </div>  </div> <div> <a href="/insights/customer/yapi-kredi" class="button _button_sdu2i_5 _tertiary_sdu2i_89 astro-xmfm7fui"><span class="_label_sdu2i_51 label astro-xmfm7fui">View Customer Story</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="19.807" height="17.934" viewBox="0 0 19.807 17.934" class="_btn-arrow_sdu2i_57 btn-arrow astro-xmfm7fui" data-icon="btn-arrow">  <use  xlink:href="#icon-btn-arrow"></use>   </svg></a> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="swiper-pagination"></div> <div class="swiper-arrow"> <div class="swiper-button-next"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="19.807" height="17.934" viewBox="0 0 19.807 17.934" data-icon="btn-arrow">  <use  xlink:href="#icon-btn-arrow"></use>   </svg></div> <div class="swiper-button-prev"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="19.807" height="17.934" viewBox="0 0 19.807 17.934" data-icon="btn-arrow">  <use  xlink:href="#icon-btn-arrow"></use>   </svg></div> </div> </div> </section> </quote-slider> <content-featured-resources variation="" paddingBottom="true"><section class="_featured_block_rl7hj_1 resource-block section-padding-bottom"><div class="container"><div class="_featuredheading_rl7hj_1"><h2 class="_heading_title_rl7hj_19 text-center section-heading" id="featured-resources">Learn, evaluate, implement</h2></div><div class="_resources_card_variant_three_rl7hj_69"><div class="_image-card_rl7hj_51" style="position:relative">  <a href="https://techzone.omnissa.com/omnissa-access" target="_blank" class="button _nostyle_sdu2i_1 _image_with_text_card_1ao6a_151 _card_layout_1ao6a_1 _image-card_rl7hj_51 astro-xmfm7fui"> <div> <picture>  <img src="https://static.omnissa.com/sites/default/files/styles/image_to_webp/public/Omnissa_default_Tall_Thumbnail_Image.jpg.webp" width="358" height="433" loading="lazy" decoding="async" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true"> </picture> </div> <div class="_right_col_1ao6a_180"> <div class="_col-tag-icon_1ao6a_258"> <div class="_tag_1ao6a_13">Webpage</div>  </div> <h3 class="_heading_title_1ao6a_209 h5-size">Omnissa Access technical overview</h3> <p class="_description_1ao6a_96">Designed to provide your employees with faster access to SaaS, web and native mobile apps with multi-factor authentication, conditional access and single sign-on.</p> <div class="_inner_col_1ao6a_127"> <button href="https://techzone.omnissa.com/omnissa-access" target="_blank" class="button _button_sdu2i_5 _tertiary_sdu2i_89 _read_more_link_1ao6a_16 astro-xmfm7fui"><span class="_label_sdu2i_51 label astro-xmfm7fui">Learn More</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="19.807" height="17.934" viewBox="0 0 19.807 17.934" class="_btn-arrow_sdu2i_57 btn-arrow astro-xmfm7fui" data-icon="btn-arrow">  <use  xlink:href="#icon-btn-arrow"></use>   </svg></button> <div class="_icon_1ao6a_19"> <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="25.806" height="25.806" viewBox="0 0 25.806 25.806" data-icon="[object Object]">   <path fill="currentColor" d="M21.619 21.427A12.073 12.073 0 1 0 4.18 21.42a.7.7 0 0 0 .161.282.8.8 0 0 0 .268.154 12.013 12.013 0 0 0 16.647 0 .6.6 0 0 0 .262-.154.6.6 0 0 0 .1-.275ZM2.201 13.801h3.32a18.4 18.4 0 0 0 .9 5.238 12 12 0 0 0-1.57 1.187A10.7 10.7 0 0 1 2.202 13.8ZM4.85 6.034a12 12 0 0 0 1.57 1.187 18.4 18.4 0 0 0-.9 5.238H2.168a10.68 10.68 0 0 1 2.683-6.426Zm18.781 6.426h-3.354a18.3 18.3 0 0 0-.9-5.232 13 13 0 0 0 1.57-1.194 10.68 10.68 0 0 1 2.683 6.426ZM13.57 2.48c1.637.356 3.085 1.925 4.065 4.165a10.7 10.7 0 0 1-4.065 1.12Zm-1.341 5.285a10.6 10.6 0 0 1-4.091-1.12c.986-2.234 2.461-3.85 4.091-4.179Zm0 1.341v3.354H6.863a17 17 0 0 1 .778-4.561 11.8 11.8 0 0 0 4.588 1.211Zm0 4.7v3.387a11.8 11.8 0 0 0-4.595 